### ========================================
### NOTES AND USAGE INSTRUCTIONS
### ========================================

### This file demonstrates:
### 1. Basic Usage: Simple caching and request context
### 2. Intermediate Usage: Device detection, circuit breakers, health monitoring
### 3. Enterprise Usage: Multi-tenant support, security, comprehensive monitoring
### 4. Advanced Patterns: Hybrid caching, resilience, adaptive content
### 5. Testing: Different devices, tenants, client IDs, and error scenarios

### To use this file:
### 1. Set the {{baseUrl}} variable to your API base URL
### 2. Set {{authToken}} to a valid authentication token
### 3. Set {{adminToken}} to a valid admin authentication token
### 4. Run the requests to test different scenarios

### Key Features Demonstrated:
### - Caching strategies (basic, intermediate, enterprise)
### - Circuit breaker patterns
### - Device detection and adaptive content
### - Multi-tenant isolation
### - Security headers and policies
### - Health monitoring
### - Error handling and resilience
### - Performance optimization
